title: Pop band "The Vamps" visit Milton Keynes to sign copies of new single | Anglia
text:
The Vamps Credit: PA Fans of the pop band The Vamps will get to meet the singers as the guys are due in Milton Keynes this afternoon.
They'll be visiting HMV in the town to celebrate the release of their single and signing copies for their fans.
The store were tweeting fans yesterday advising them not to turn up to early.
HMV Milton Keynes @HmvMiltonKeynes Follow The Vamps will be signing copies of their new single "Wake Up" in our store at 5pm tomorrow. (1 of 2) http://t.co/xAyCXPOFrf
16:42 - 1 Oct 2015 Retweet Reply Favourite HMV Milton Keynes @HmvMiltonKeynes Follow We'd advise queueing no earlier than 4pm for the event. The band aim to meet everyone. (2 of 2)
